[SN]TITLE[SN]
Binali Yildirim - farmer's son who became prime minister

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
New Turkish Prime Minister Binali Yildirim's political career began while he managed Istanbul's ferry bus network at a time when current President Recep Tayyip Erdogan was mayor.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
23 May 2016 Last updated at 17:21 BST
He has since become the Turkish leader's right-hand man.
Here we trace his rise to power.
